## 2. Glossary
- **data-wid** — stable semantic element ID injected at build time: `{slide}-{role}-{ordinal}`.
- **Version chain** — ordered sequence `_v0 → _v1 → _vN`; each version is one HTML artifact
  (`_vN.html`) plus the feedback that produced it (`_vN.md`).
- **Feedback item** — one targeted edit: `{selector, type, instruction, before}`.
- **type enum** — `content-edit` | `style-edit` | `structural-change`.
- **Working head** — the version currently shown and edited against.

